        "action": "UK Government should work with Dumfries and Galloway Council to house refugees",
        "additional_details": "Countries close to war torn countries have begun to refuse letting in refugees. It is a selfish act to deprive others of the things we take for granted every day. Let refugees come here.",
        "background": "Many refugees live in awful horrible conditions and we do not. There is so much space here in Dumfries and Galloway and I want the refugees to have the same opportunities that we have. ",
